   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>... (I have not received ?) a letter from you. So deign to write me at some point concerning your health. For  have I not written to you once,  twice, many times enquiring about your state of health. For there is nothing else causing me sorrow apart from this. For I heard here that something distressing has happened to me -  you know about what. I greet your ladies mothers and your brothers. Were you not given to my heart ("to my consolation" Preisendanz)? Were you not put ("put to sleep" Schmidt) under (my ?) head-cover? Were you not made by my mother  to share my bundle/coverlet?;Verso:;To Kam... (from?) Apoll(onia ?), the daughter of Theodoros</ab>
         </div>
